name: Rock Star Brass Butterfly Necklace
description:
We love the rockin' vibe of this large 'rock star butterfly' necklace + we've deemed it the essential accessory for you rebellious babes out there. Our rockin' butterfly with her trademark cut-out star, is hand-cut from brass, filed + given a satin finish. She flutters around on a 'dirty' (slightly oxidized) sterling silver chain that closes with an oxidized sterling silver spring clasp.


►1.5" x 1.5" hand-cut brass butterfly pendant.


Made to order. Our brass pieces are treated to resist tarnish.


Handmade in Toronto

name: Brass Arrow Bracelet - Personalized
description:
Cool + chic, our brass arrow bracelet is hand cut, filed, polished + hand stamped with your name. Our arrow shaped tag is attached to a flat round link gunmetal chain that sparkles when it catches the light. Finishes with a large gunmetal lobster clasp. Layer with other bracelets for an awesome arm-y. 



►7" total length.
►brass arrow tag - 40mm (L) x 10mm (w).
►space for 5 characters across. 
►available in CAP LETTERS only.
►name can be posted in the note to seller box at check out.


Our brass pieces are treated to resist tarnish. Use a jewelry polishing cloth occasionally to maintain the shine.

**Please note all customized initial + personalized pieces are final sale + cannot be returned or refunded.


Handmade in Toronto
